; M3 gate: step-vector macro engine (slice 1). One VOL macro with an attack
; step, a :hold sustain loop, and an :off release section. Exercises trigger
; on NOTE_ON, the sustain loop under a held note, the release region when the
; note keys off into a rest, macro re-trigger on the next note, and
; MACRO_CLEAR (the tail notes carry no macro).
(fm1 :tempo 150 :alg 4 :fb 3 :ar1 31 :tl1 20 :ar4 31 :tl4 8
  (macro :vol [28 :hold 22 18 :off 14 10 6 4]) :len 4
  c _ e (macro :vol none) g c)
